### EduPortal API - Accommodation Arrangements Controller
### Study abroad accommodation management endpoints
### Base URL: http://localhost:5000
### Requires Authentication

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api/accommodation-arrangements
@contentType = application/json
@token = {{$dotenv TOKEN}}

### ===========================================
### GET ALL ARRANGEMENTS - (Admin, Coach, Danışman)
### ===========================================
GET {{baseUrl}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===========================================
### GET ACTIVE ARRANGEMENTS - (Admin, Coach, Danışman)
### ===========================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/active
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===========================================
### GET ARRANGEMENT SUMMARIES - (Admin, Coach, Danışman)
### ===========================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/summaries
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===========================================
### GET ARRANGEMENT BY ID - (Admin, Coach, Danışman, Ogrenci)
### ===========================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===========================================
### GET ARRANGEMENTS BY PROGRAM - (Admin, Coach, Danışman, Ogrenci)
### ===========================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/program/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===========================================
### GET ACCOMMODATION STATISTICS - (Admin, Coach, Danışman)
### ===========================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/statistics
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===========================================
### CREATE ARRANGEMENT - (Admin, Coach, Danışman)
### ===========================================
POST {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "studyAbroadProgramId": 1,
  "accommodationType": "Dormitory",
  "facilityName": "University Residence Hall",
  "address": "123 Campus Drive, Boston, MA",
  "checkInDate": "2024-08-25",
  "checkOutDate": "2025-05-15",
  "monthlyRent": 1200.00,
  "isPaid": false,
  "notes": "Tek kişilik oda"
}

### ===========================================
### UPDATE ARRANGEMENT - (Admin, Coach, Danışman)
### ===========================================
PUT {{baseUrl}}/1
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "monthlyRent": 1250.00,
  "isPaid": true,
  "notes": "Ödeme tamamlandı"
}

### ===========================================
### DELETE ARRANGEMENT - (Admin only)
### ===========================================
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

